{"word":"G1737 - ἐνδιδύσκω - endidýskō - en-did-oos'-ko - Clothe in","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνδιδύσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">endidýskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-did-oos'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Clothe in</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வஸ்திரந்தரி"},{"paragraph":"to put on, clothe"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of <a href=\"#/G1746 - ἐνδύω - endýō - en-doo'-o/1746\">G1746</a>; to <i>invest</i> (with a garment): - clothe in, wear.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}